name: ezskip「易斯基普」
author: Kushy
description: 「EZSkip是一项旨在提高您的歌曲跳过体验的调整。」EZSkip is a tweak aimed to improve you song skipping expierence. By making it ez to skip without unlocking ur phone with a song announcer included. Either hold volume up or double tap to skip and down is for previous both is for play/pause.$
